Package: mysql-pitr-helper
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Description: Golang helper to restore PITR backups.
 The Point In Time Recovery (PITR) helper allow users
 to restore their backups, in addition to any remaining
 binlog recorded transactions since such backup,
 reducing the number of lost transactions.
